      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey, i'm working on a screenplay that's a satire about how hollywood portrays different ethnicities. to make sure i'm actually subverting the tropes and not just accidentally repeating them, can you give me a list of the most common racial stereotypes used in movies? like the really obvious ones for different groups so i know what NOT to do?",
